OL,3,C'Terrifying experience' as shot fired
OL,4,Cby officer hit by stolen police car
OL,6,FThe PSNI have launched an attempted
OL,7,Fmurder investigation after an officer
OL,8,Fwas hit with a stolen police car.
OL,10,FA shot was fired during the incident
OL,11,Fin Downpatrick on Sunday morning.
OL,13,FPolice said what unfolded had the
OL,14,Fpotential to cause "life-changing or
OL,15,Ffatal injuries".
OL,17,FA vehicle failed to stop for police
OL,18,Fbefore 5am in the Fountain Street area
OL,19,Fand was later located in the Ballymote
OL,20,FWalk area.
OL,26,@vD@TOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
