CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780405872
OL,3,C'Terrifying experience' as shot fired
OL,4,Cby officer hit by stolen police car
OL,6,FA man was then seen running from the
OL,7,Fvehicle and a foot pursuit ensued
OL,8,Ftowards the Colmcille Road.
OL,10,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Melanie
OL,11,FJones said: "As officers returned to
OL,12,Ftheir police car, someone was in the
OL,13,Fdriver's seat ` driving erratically
OL,14,Fand directly towards an officer.
OL,16,F"The officer discharged one round from
OL,17,Fhis firearm.
OL,19,F"The officer was struck by the vehicle
OL,20,F` causing serious injuries.
OL,26,@sD@MOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780405872
OL,3,C'Terrifying experience' as shot fired
OL,4,Cby officer hit by stolen police car
OL,6,F"The vehicle was subsequently
OL,7,Fabandoned a short time later. The
OL,8,Fsuspect made off from the scene.
OL,10,F"Urgent medical treatment was provided
OL,11,Fat the scene by police colleagues, who
OL,12,Fwere also supported by members of the
OL,13,Flocal community.
OL,15,F"The officer was taken to hospital by
OL,16,Fcolleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,17,FAmbulance Service for treatment to his
OL,18,Finjuries believed to be serious, but
OL,19,Fthankfully not life-threatening at
OL,20,Fthis time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780405872
OL,3,C'Terrifying experience' as shot fired
OL,4,Cby officer hit by stolen police car
OL,6,F"As part of our enquiries, a 27-year-
OL,7,Fold man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder and remains in
OL,9,Fcustody at this time."
OL,11,FShe added: "Officers put themselves on
OL,12,Fthe front line to help keep people
OL,13,Fsafe ` they do not deserve to be
OL,14,Fassaulted for simply doing their job,
OL,15,Fand today's incident is a stark
OL,16,Freminder of the dangers they face.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]sD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780405872
OL,3,C'Terrifying experience' as shot fired
OL,4,Cby officer hit by stolen police car
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with the officer as
OL,7,Fhe receives ongoing medical treatment
OL,8,Ftoday for his injuries in hospital.
OL,9,FAnd we will continue to support him
OL,10,Fand his family.
OL,12,F"This would have been a terrifying
OL,13,Fexperience for the officer and also
OL,14,Fhis colleagues ` with the clear
OL,15,Fpotential to cause life-changing or
OL,16,Feven fatal injuries.
OL,18,F"Actions were taken this morning in
OL,19,Fdefence of life to protect himself and
OL,20,Ffellow officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780405872
OL,3,C'Terrifying experience' as shot fired
OL,4,Cby officer hit by stolen police car
OL,6,F"Detectives from our Serious Crime
OL,7,Fbranch have now launched an attempted
OL,8,Fmurder investigation ` with their
OL,9,Fenquiries continuing at pace."
OL,11,FThe police vehicle, weapon and
OL,12,Fammunition have all been recovered and
OL,13,Fremoved for forensic examination.
OL,15,FThe Police Ombudsman confirmed it had
OL,16,Fbeen notified of the firing of a
OL,17,Fround, and its investigators attended
OL,18,Fthe scene.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
